#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:1
msgid "Convert tz-aware Datetime Array/Index from one time zone to another."
msgstr "将具有时区信息的 Datetime Array/Index 从一个时区转换为另一个时区。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:3
msgid ""
"Time zone for time. Corresponding timestamps would be converted to this "
"time zone of the Datetime Array/Index. A `tz` of None will convert to UTC"
" and remove the timezone information."
msgstr ""
"时间的时区。相应的 时间戳 将被转换为 Datetime Array/Index 的此 时区。`tz`"
" 为 None 时将转换为 UTC 并移除时区信息。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:10
msgid "If Datetime Array/Index is tz-naive."
msgstr "如果 Datetime Array/Index 是不具有时区信息的。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:14
msgid ":py:obj:`DatetimeIndex.tz`"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:15
msgid "A timezone that has a variable offset from UTC."
msgstr "一个与 UTC 具有可变偏移量的时区。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:17
msgid ":py:obj:`DatetimeIndex.tz_localize`"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:18
msgid ""
"Localize tz-naive DatetimeIndex to a given time zone, or remove timezone "
"from a tz-aware DatetimeIndex."
msgstr ""
"将不具有时区信息的 DatetimeIndex 本地化为给定时区，或从具有时区信息的 "
"DatetimeIndex 中移除时区。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:21
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

