msgid ""
"With the `tz` parameter, we can change the DatetimeIndex to other time "
"zones:"
msgstr "使用 `tz` 参数，我们可以将 DatetimeIndex 更改为其他时区："

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:41
msgid ""
"With the ``tz=None``, we can remove the timezone (after converting to UTC"
" if necessary):"
msgstr "使用 ``tz=None``，我们可以移除时区（如有必要会在转换为 UTC 后进行）："

